Starring:

Director:
Howard McCain
Synopsis:
When an extraterrestrial spaceship comes crashing down to Earth during 
the reign of the Vikings, the Scandinavian plunderers get set to do 
battle with a most unusual enemy in director Howard McCain's earthbound 
science fiction thriller. Jim Caviezel, Jack Huston, and Sophia Myles 
star in a film scripted by director McCain in collaboration 
with screenwriter Dirk Blackman.
